*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* EVENT HANDLER
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
CLASS lcl_event_handler DEFINITION.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS on_user_command
      FOR EVENT added_function OF cl_salv_events_table
      IMPORTING e_salv_function.
ENDCLASS.
